Class Square

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cpp.cs.cs141.final_project.Square
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Hallway, Room

    public abstract class Square
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class represents a square on the Board. It is an abstract class and can be specialized to be a Room or a Hallway.
